setTypeMapping

public void setTypeMapping(java.lang.String typeMapping)
Sets the class name of products in this mapping configuration of generated class Saada, and creates the object modelling the mapping type used in this configuration. If the mapping type (the value in parameter) is the name of the loaded product in configuration file, the used mode is the user mode.

Parameters:
String - The name of mapping type, or the class name in user mode.
